p: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;特朗普正在寻求一项自国会在大萧条期间创建以来一直未使用的关税权力&lt;/strong&gt;。在最高法院驳回他违反宪法使用紧急权力法发动全球贸易战后，这位共和党人一直在寻找其他方式来&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/vIfPYTNFyXwigLjuss_Z-c33U-c3X99jxMuUITISWshFTdECLDBx0NdESuZsXH2LIzkSbc3CzUSFPnWvch6vtDVXuPuo-RSTWw3M3Q6Nj0TOa6uObtdymjykgube0SQa5vnc6pEC4e2NXZbcpiMbn8t0MncKfeQb_VmdHyfqMqSFKjR3YgSkBF2K2dZyawJ2e4mCtvIBx3uex6gdwMvMyn5CRz6F8Gj5LcgVcaCzdrT2G0nsTKFDXH4rFsxlR_e6YdmFCE3oAiGcAUJ9XU6Rn09Vsp4PDCS5YM3Xt2W8K0uPEF3QVBbzNg/-tmjODnT13tcicPJGgyDYaRT7J6nN4Tj/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普称关税是字典中“对我来说最美丽的词”"&gt;追求他对关税的热爱&lt;/a&gt;——这种爱好让&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/xm8CXPMFBbSlY4ztxxrAURWlmbbvRGjdp0_UVPHKFWVTZV_q1EQNFOuFihrrJQiyV7ZcWmnBqGEBQXqWA2sX4By2PqjQZVxvOnwtILRcw5wmvAhr7-5jUUK37FOxxl1joyWFjRspc6vktabNzgXdD4aVpjM3ai6TiEUV2MHqnMUWyXUOywWx2vKvqVjM5tIP_yz8gQUAEKuIRN4OF0Fbm42wlrZOjIMjXvJzPPm6WP_j9CPq0oDJT9t6MHoScTiYK06tYyKK8wh_yBpzHU8dntMc4wJkOmgywq7bEfP_vnWAsR9bqVnQS3rU7VZMcscMpp84F-m1kzkjw9CH1OpJ0Ddw9KyUV5phwhDYs2RZ-9VMkEc/n3btP7phAA1atV1px0ixqtwqSDps2fvq/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="关税提高了消费者的价格，但退款只流向企业"&gt;美国企业和消费者付出了&lt;/a&gt;代价。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;现在，他转向援引 1930 年关税法第 338 条， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/CJ3_BM5KqzhDVgt1QfuGTVKZ6yYRfs_O6zLdtLAkxQ7Xcn2xVcaYeDXrI1LeNEvLlZ5OaUB0qFyw_m6Way9DAzltdn5UzhAHV-utH-g2ydFx3a7vIncu3Y-kUaSvAH953gvd3jr6evzlWGfHYSjYqT8SOJKDcqw-PvIqMBA457XUFbMacljX8LgY31QMVOOyO_q8tNkt-_isd2fae6_1IFU8HkVTHqk40abdcnOfJpUQSzQpiyxdld4XiBiP4xDxy1WUZmS5cJJEn0dFN3csUmnJ6UQuQ8fij6bRm2-7tZAqlLt6MFKJLpZpOo_8BfJXblM6TsTSbnyiKMob_ZSxd3v4-EMEGOy3HojM2_jbeY9ZbSPH8srSG8ZeiwOVmq6JGqeEGthjGcIkjSoeflib0kFKPyXh1F83CXEVQ4Cg8wIrPdGczITZAqVt5uhVv4DYt3ggkw7uUb-yQqAn5h0T2gqBU2BBhBKw5T9nvaf6t0mlcePT92Qj2iHN5Y88buzlA1NaJu5T81DCxylF7or-DTIPVOPPsg/4CCez4KcsWRmexz-cuy72lPwu9wOoQyq/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;威胁对来自美国以前友好邻国的某些进口商品征收 50% 的关税&lt;/a&gt;。这项晦涩的条款赋予总统广泛的权力，可以针对美国商业的歧视性待遇征收关税，但其使用可能会引发新的法律挑战。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/cpVOz0doTWE9qQZuFWV49ewbtr7RDlTrav6Q0DDzRHjXaqlWvNvYPBmdY1YqOlaSWf8kjq3DMoMriSNlxSEpjc08H7yHtNBRgIrjVqKd3gQMm5e-xfpqvtsE2KPP6UfRn5geAw7065yTW_EmOJorD0rMakzH3YymtZq4Wf4vNA7sgILT7avg3kobDPxORuMcSqjwhjFxezi22DVHN64Z_H0Sky-twl173h-wH0iLWWzFku5YANpq2ThASIzcGHCIenHE_8vkfCXwdHHGTJJzCJR1S9lh3H7JhfBDVsXnV9D0niFzhorFpmbFI4skXBZKqQ6hJonmCmjrEWDQscDzD6t-mZcr0LsbEkBKuJnKTgFfz0rxyvBf9_8X3FQ5sWa3lh4ge-wpZSJFacMljOElI2WdiWa9FUc1fAnjnCh5TAJlasUANeNc-ZVlMQSEvbcazTWVYnz2AAc3rp2YqGvU1_gCcvO1TEKGJIm90e7sARwA_Xuir-VXMbYVNRb3lThdquSOK19JirbWJbMenRgnfcv3KZExj_AfEBW59HM5ssUrWIaqmw/cAOEaf78Dd6_LeInQNncVD26vkeAcGKn/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普为何利用百年法律以 50% 关税威胁加拿大"&gt;以下是您需要了解的信息&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 24px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/vMxr6m60Hq2JRhOiQhCjTh_sGXoojiaJ4NqIClZQSj_5-u81rKilSsC6hjHjj_7U2VDgKo5yEDPwckQdro68jfaXRiMi5yxrk1NbGYceSxuKb8r-xpArB9EF-o2SjAn3jOD0fqbN_lWOh8z0nnf_YSy5OQdjuxrzLvv8sodiO8vM4v_3WSsgdr3M8iKpwS6UJ3ydkLmJVTOEbKZO_J_OoIGt7j7z8u_boWmJuDoRL4QUQfsMvzk3suFLLtrAeQqDtyzclCLllwWTKWW5iBd32crG4BjU1IFeNq6Y42jM9aLcX5ITewexhSOgz4BYtzMs9FsBlo_WKKW_D85QJ5wpY5FMGrZ1MbTw02ml-e7ACxBiKIBDK4gqZiiyjQ-aGcTZpSqQVqveQUkx6sFSjGoOBFNibU_k0KCHc42uppRg2GJO-04kB3-HdhE2ek1L6TuiYGb5quwZDpJZ1ZPTMu-0IMZvMUvYZLV5LfOqlHHcnoBW5c3R_H6krpsGvnCobEpmvNSbVutdLFK67Q/IiZT5dkmljZPCwsxJ1zmXN1GvkYSUZRE/22" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 0 0 24px 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;彭博社观点&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="line-height: normal; font-weight: 700; margin: 12px 0 0 0; font-size: 20px !important;"&gt;世界上最愚蠢的关税变得更加愚蠢&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: 1.4; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;罗伯特·伯吉斯 (Robert Burgess) 写道，今年早些时候，他的同事斯科特·林西科姆 (Scott Lincicome) 提出了令人信服的理由，说明为什么对美国铝进口征收关税可能是特朗普政府所有关税中最愚蠢的一项。伯吉斯说，本周事情变得更加愚蠢。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 40px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; border: 1px solid; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;阅读更多&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;对于那些投入真金白银的人来说&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;，这些可笑的钱不再是一件可笑的事情&lt;/strong&gt;—— &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/TBkMwgmenMoiHYGh0KsP6OyZn1jnDbMO1SJWTxO2UUMKQCR5AMvQTOFRfeMBaogTgve6aC47y0ZFfPOYFNkPYhgAlbZXaPnwpiBSHntWcKGHLFbhgzeGY0hhUF9_aSi6-RSyo_2ib4qQTWtm78eu0SNgWBBgpBxyBOeUxyPokXDx8vvN-wqM4GHxvUDb3gxllY_UHGd7ZEI_A8Ag3YwV7CKpQ7Mvs82qFQyWzXyOVA6riinMoTV__fL5xebxWUYTC--O6fqoOmnoQeTvZDrqIHNbzVRBWB5tgtWPAaK5u7_RONMryCjzXKFyqXxO7KW1L0wiCiGWqHb6pYcE9ltzLcqnEbMV14-tw5bzBrblklPMyi0XVkm2eNfGHA85EUeHfwHLgtpOGu2JoUh4oIl2Wj1Om-jlTsZ_Q-LGvO6-94plHQ0PFi46Be8J8Tn7cd5k-2gpX2jBRFUKtJkhTS_6GZvmTO-71lsXQVGpPfG6pFPUl5Bc_-YI0i2IV1XCyYCpZxzbc0b60P0hm1f8nO6qMsnvhvih2g/IxVDCAXCmSGiXI4vAa69vl7uPL1WQM3r/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="比特币暴跌正在压垮储存代币的公司"&gt;对某些人来说，比其他人更是如此&lt;/a&gt;。自 10 月份比特币达到顶峰以来，当时加密货币友好型白宫的到来，狂热者们仍在蜂拥而至，但这种数字货币已经下跌了一半。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;目前其交易价格约为 66,000 美元，低于特朗普 2024 年 11 月大选时的价格。当然，这对加密货币投资者来说是不利的，但对所谓的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/5GVGd8v6TSbDyZhp3p4C9YlcUumkKFg48fxxL7O2ZrKqnt_-Q9dHW4uUJWn1yiCjV89JdkUAkI7W4GZ4zpTUPscvvlngdyNCjjKRWyJfT7ZNnJ9QS-a1UnBVEmY